Text:
@IndigoAK: way to go moron... maybe figure out what you are talking about before you post.  The patch is not supposed to make the cursor look like your desktop cursor.  It uses the desktop cursor with the XCOM graphics which removes lag and makes it much more responsive but looks identical.

CONFIRM: yes this patch fixes the cursor.  Also fixes the videos.  Implementation of other fixes are harder to confirm though.

Retards who do not know what they are talking about: please go home

@Axedal: Yes, I see that now.  I stand corrected.

There are still all kinds of performance issues even with the patch though, so hopefully Firaxis has more of them coming.

Also, the mouse cursor doesn't seem to disappear completely when using the 360 controller anymore.  I have to hide it in the corner.
